damage.defaultValue: no damage nor permanent malfunction to be observed

cont-open.defaultValue: no closed-contact circuit open for a duration exceeding 10?s

cont-close.defaultValue: no open-contact circuit closed for a period exceeding 10?s

description:
code for the criteria for evaluation of resistance of relays to shock and vibration.
The criterion 'cont-open' covers both of the other criteria, the criterion 'cont-close' covers the criterion 'damage'.
